phrases: Even if those dreams will be scary
As long as I am looking at
I have been looking for you
the only thing that was scrambled
in the middle of our heartbeats,
if only that was our destiny...
Based on The Sanzu River ( O Sanzu-no-kawa ), or River of Three Crossings.
Most Japanese people believe that on the way to the afterlife, the dead must cross the river.
Kopi Luwak Coffee is the most expensive coffee in the world, selling between S120 and S600 USD per pound.
What is going to happen next?
It will be the same no matter where we go.
As long as the Kishin lives, the world will be controlled by madness.
I am beginning to wonder if it was Medusa's intention to bring down an opponent like that.
Are you talking about the Kishin?
No matter who that is, it will still be impossible, right?
You do understand, right, Black Star?
This is where we must hold out.
This has nothing to do with holding out.
Because the one who is going to defeat him is none other than ME!
I am so glad to see you.
It is still too early to be glad.
I have relied too much on the Black Blood.
Thanks to that, I am now locked up in this room.
Most of my soul has been consumed by the insanity of the Black Blood.
That is why I am here to get you.
Let us get out of this place as soon as possible.
The door disappeared the moment you got in.
Any other way to get out?
I would have been long gone if there were any.
Well, you got a point there...
Let us break through the wall.
We will rip out the tiles and dig us a tunnel!
Thanks for the massage - I am all refreshed now.
I think even my voice has gotten clearer now.
If this continues, we will lose our foothold.
Did I hear you say foothold?
Such things as footholds never existed!
When facing an overwhelming power such as mine,
it is impossible for unpredictable things to happen.
As of the question of what is to become of you,
it had already been decided when you came inside this barrier.
I would hate to admit it,
but with this level of attacks,
I do not think it is possible to put even a scratch on you.
Then we will use attacks of higher levels!
I was unable to understand your true intentions.
And I doubted Shibusen's every move.
I am responsible for your defeat against the Kishin.
If there was a hole somewhere, I would hide in it.
If only I was not so distrustful,
then things would have surely played out differently.
might be no more than an overstatement.
In the name of the Shinigami, I will purge you!
Liz, Patty, let us do this!
Take a look at Kid's soul.
follow my lead and back me up.
Are you going to steal my spotlight at a crucial time like this?!
This is no time for you to fool around!
We must make sure that my next shot hits him.
Until I am ready, I will need you to hold him back.
I am going to give it my all with this next shot.
And there will be no second shots.
I do not like the way you put it.
First, I will charge right at him,
and you will go on with your preparation and back me up when you are done!
I am going to be the main character until the end!
I would appreciate it if you could handle it with care,
cuz that is my courage that is in there.
It is not my courage that is in here.
It is myself that is in here!
Due to the effect of the Black Blood, my courage has been sealed up inside this box.
I should be able to get us both out of here.
I sealed myself in right before the Black Blood could completely take over my soul.
If you open it, my soul will be completely consumed by the Black Blood!
No matter how hard I tried, I could not get it open.
He is just trying to trick you into opening this box so that he can get in and consume what is left of me!
That is not me, it is that small demon!
But Maka, I believe you are the one who can open it.
If I open this, then you will be able to get out of here, right?
The key is in your hand.
You idiot, do not listen to him!
That is not right of you, blaming it on me.
It was you who came butting into my barrier.
Why did your soul turn into something like this?!
I do not really know what is happening, but this is kind of cool!
Guess we will just have to do whatever we can for now!
You are the son of that Shinigami.
Allow me to get rid of you before things gets ugly.
It is not him, but me who is going to kick your ass!
Do not even think of taking your eyes off me!
Do not take your eyes off me!
Did not I just tell you that I am right here?!
To defeat you, I must at least be capable of doing this!
But that was really one hell of a shot.
He is the Kid we know.
He is not going to die from just that.
Tsubaki, do not give me that shocked look.
This can only mean one thing, right?
it is really my destiny to surpass God!
The only thing that we know of, so far,
is that there is now one more crack in Shinigami-sama's mask.
Yeah, but not looking very well, I must say.
Azusa, cannot you use your Clairvoyance to take a look at what is going on inside?
I am afraid it is not possible.
It is just impossible with my ability.
Then, it is also possible that the battle is already over...
The battle is still going on.
Then you can see what is going on inside?
I would like to have a cup of coffee before answering that.
Hey everyone, what is the commotion?
It seems that I caused everyone a lot of trouble.
Do you think it is the right time for that?
Maka, Kid and Black Star are battling with the Kishin inside that barrier.
So I was right to say that the key element is going to be-
If you are not going to open it, I will do it myself!
I am not going to give you this key.
I am Soul, inside and out!
Soul would never ask me something like that!
It is because there is no other way that I am asking you to do it!
Then why did you close the door when I came in?
Soul would never do something like that!
He would have asked me to turn back if he knew we would be locked in here.
You are not the idiot I thought you were!
Certainly, I am not the Soul that you have always known.
but I am also a genuine Soul Eater, you know.
I am a part of Soul, and he is a part of me.
We are the same, Soul and I, in a single body.
It is like partners that you cannot separate even if you cut us in two.
That is why, when you say that I am not Soul, you are correct, but at the same time you are incorrect.
Like you have made a mistake, but at the same time you have not.
Do not you find it funny?
To think that some one as arrogant as him ends up inside such a small box.
He is just getting in the way.
As things are now, the whole world is almost in my possession already.
Like the time when you let yourself go berserk, just let me take care of everything.
Not only the size, nor the outside or the inside, but everything!
It will not mean anything if you do not open it now.
Because if you do not, Soul and I will die soon enough.
There is only two choices to choose from.
Either you keep the box closed and watch him die,
or open the box and meet the Soul who has been completely taken over by insanity one more time.
Soul is really in here, right?
Have not you paid attention to anything he is said?!
As I thought, you are not the type to abandon your partner, right?
I am not going to let Soul be taken over by insanity.
I am definitely going to rescue him!
So much of an idiot that it makes you the coolest partner I can ever have.
so I am brought back into this good-for-nothing world?
What are you getting so worked up about?
You thinking of getting rid of me?!
Who would do such a thing?
I am just going to accept you as you are.
Where are Kid and Black Star?
There is nothing for you to feel strange about.
The chosen ones in the chosen place.
The chosen ones suffer defeat and they fall.
There is nothing so unexpected or interesting about something like that.
Of course, that includes fear itself.
